data.description: Must see!! Come see this oversized, 4 bed, 3 bath, Ranch Style home that sits on almost 1/4 acre! This home boasts vaulted ceilings, large bedrooms and tons of open space for the family. With a recently replaced roof and solar panels installed, it will help cut down utility bills and give you peace of mind. Don't miss out. Schedule your showing today!
